```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuario
    participant ST as Streamlit
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant SVC as App Service
    participant OCR as OCR Service
    participant AI as AI Service
    participant RE as Rules Engine
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant OL as Ollama

    U->>ST: Llena formulario
    ST->>API: POST /applications
    API->>SVC: create_application()
    SVC->>DB: Guardar solicitud
    DB-->>SVC: App ID
    SVC-->>ST: Respuesta

    U->>ST: Sube documento
    ST->>API: POST /applications/{id}/documents
    API->>SVC: upload_document()
    SVC->>OCR: extract_text()
    OCR->>OCR: pymupdf
    OCR->>OCR: Tesseract
    OCR-->>SVC: texto extraído
    
    SVC->>AI: extract_document_info()
    AI->>OL: Ollama LLM
    OL-->>AI: JSON con datos
    AI-->>SVC: datos extraídos
    
    SVC->>RE: evaluate_application()
    RE-->>SVC: aprobado/rechazado
    SVC->>DB: Actualizar estado
    DB-->>SVC: OK
    SVC-->>ST: Resultado final
```
